data.title: Defender Spawn to A Generator Fault Line
data.description: This is a good fault line for A Site to stun and concuss anyone playing on-top of A Generator

data.title: B Main to Top B Green Aftershock
data.description: This is a good aftershock to get your opponent out of the common spot ontop of B Green.

data.title: B Garage to B Green Flashpoint
data.description: This is a good flash to blind anyone peeking B Garage from B Green or B Yellow.

data.title: A Screens to A Site Flashpoint
data.description: This is a good flashpoint for back A Site from the front side of A Screens.

data.title: A Pipes to A Site Aftershock
data.description: This is a good aftershock to prevent enemies from defusing the bomb.

data.title: A Nest to A Pipes Flashpoint
data.description: This is a good flashpoint for A Pipes to blind both sides allowing you to swing and get a kill.

data.title: A Nest to A Generator Aftershock
data.description: This is a good aftershock for A Site to force enemies out of the A Generator corner.

data.title: A Belt Through A Nest Flashpoint
data.description: This flash is perfect to use when trying to push/peek from the upper area of A Site. As wall as for a defender to buy time to lurk close below the A Belt area!
